              <p class="font-size-18">With the dependents workspace, you will be able to manage multiple accounts of you and your family. The dependents workspace allows you to work as your family members or your dependents and apply for approval requests as well as reimbursement claims on behalf of them. Furthermore, you will be able to track the status of the submitted requests and get notified whenever it’s changed.</p>
